.env.*.local
.env.secrets
!.env.example
*.pem
*.key
*.p12
*.pfx
id_rsa*
id_ed25519*
*.mnemonic
*.seed
credentials*
secrets*
**/secrets/
**/private/

# Wallet / lab local state (seeds, descriptors with keys, consignments with private data)
.lwk/
.rgbmvp/
data/
state/
wallets/
consignments/
proofs/
*.wallet
*.rgbc
*.consignment
